---
// Partner section
---

<section class="section partner-section">
  <div class="cesis_container">
    <div class="row partner-row">
      <div class="col-sm-6 partner-section__content reveal-right">
        <h2>Somos un partner para todas las agencias y consultoras que han confiado en nuestra experiencia desde 2015</h2>
        <div class="line-divider"></div>
        <p class="partner-section__subtitle">Y seguimos creciendo cada año con nuevos clientes satisfechos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="partner-section__image reveal-scale">
          <img 
            src="/images/Ilustracion_30-768x542.jpg" 
            alt="Ilustración de colaboración"
            width="768"
            height="542"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .partner-section {
    background: #f7f9fb;
  }
  
  .partner-section .row {
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .partner-section .partner-row {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }
  }
  
  .partner-section__image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .partner-section__image {
      margin-top: 24px;
      max-width: 85%;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
  }
  
  .partner-section__content {
    padding-left: 40px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .partner-section__content {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }
  
  .partner-section__content h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .partner-section__content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
    }
  }
  
  .partner-section__subtitle {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .partner-section__subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
